 Visual Technique (HDR+Glow, PointLight2D, particles/shaders)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "GAME_DESIGN.md", "source_location": "\u00a74", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Golden rule of 'game juice': every hit needs flash + particle + sound + shake + knockback to look AAA even in pixel art."}, {"id": "game_design_assets_tools", "label": "Assets and Tools (Aseprite, Kenney, freesound, Tiled)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "GAME_DESIGN.md", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "game_design_world_exploration_decision", "label": "Continuous Large Exploration World Decision", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "GAME_DESIGN.md", "source_location": "\u00a76", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "World is one large continuous map with multiple zones (crypt, dark forest, ruins) rather than separate levels; camera limits and spawners must come from the map, not be hardcoded to the player."}, {"id": "game_design_open_risks", "label": "Open Risks: Netcode, Scope, Vertical Slice", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "GAME_DESIGN.md", "source_location": "\u00a77", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Singleplayer first, multiplayer deferred but decoupled via EventBus since it is ~10x the work. Realistic first-milestone scope fixed at one map, one player, 2 enemies, 3 skills, basic loot."}], "edges": [{"source": "game_design_folder_structure", "target": "architecture_folder_structure", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.95, "source_file": "GAME_DESIGN.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "game_design_click_to_move_decision", "target": "architecture_input_actions", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score":